      "description": "Looking for a dependable vehicle with plenty of character? This car is in fair condition and ready for a driver who appreciates a solid, functional ride! It has some honest wear and tear from its journeys, but it remains a reliable companion for your daily commutes or weekend errands. With a little bit of TLC, this car has great potential to shine even brighter!",
