    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained by its previous owner. The exterior retains a nice shine, though you will find some minor stone chips on the hood and light surface scratches consistent with careful daily use. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable, with only slight wear on the driver's seat bolster and floor mats. Mechanically, the car is in great shape, starting up reliably and handling well, with a complete service history showing regular maintenance. It is a dependable choice for anyone looking for a quality vehicle that is ready for the road.",
      "price": 34500.0,
