    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle represents a premier opportunity for the discerning driver. Demonstrating consistent performance and a well-preserved interior, it offers a refined driving experience that balances sophistication with practical reliability. Our multi-point inspection confirms its sound mechanical standing and aesthetic appeal. Secure this exceptional value today.",
      "price": 31500.0,
