    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and she's been such a joy to drive! It's in really solid shape\u2014well-loved, super reliable, and runs like a dream. It\u2019s perfect for road trips or just getting around town comfortably. I\u2019ve taken great care of it, and it's totally ready for its next adventure with a new owner! Feel free to reach out with any questions at all. I'd love to see it go to a good home!",
      "price": 28500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available for acquisition is a mechanically sorted 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the iconic S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six. This unit delivers exceptional throttle response via its factory individual throttle bodies and is paired with a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox. Critical preventive maintenance has been addressed: the dual-VANOS system has been overhauled with upgraded solenoid coils and seals, and the rear subframe has been reinforced with structural plates to mitigate floor fatigue. The chassis retains its precision with a refreshed suspension setup utilizing Bilstein dampers and OEM-plus bushings. While the finish shows minor aerodynamic pitting consistent with spirited road use, the drivetrain remains tight with a functional M-Variable differential lock providing excellent corner-exit traction. This is a high-performance specimen optimized for the driver who prioritizes mechanical integrity and analog feedback.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used vehicle. Good condition. Well-maintained. Clean title. Runs smooth. Inspection reports available.",
      "price": 29500.0,
