      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This vehicle strikes the perfect balance between a well-loved driver and a meticulously maintained machine. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous finish with only the minor, expected signs of road use that speak to its history of reliable service. Inside, you\u2019ll find a smoke-free cabin featuring supple upholstery that remains firm and supportive, with all digital displays and climate controls functioning exactly as they should. Mechanically, this car is a standout; it has been serviced ahead of schedule, ensuring the engine pulls smoothly and the transmission shifts with precision. Recent maintenance includes a fresh set of premium tires and a comprehensive fluid flush. If you are looking for a vehicle that offers modern reliability and a premium feel without the new-car price tag, this is an exceptional candidate.",
      "price": 34800.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
